  Assertions
    Assertion:two-selves,sentence:two selves stand — each an Identity owning its Peering page — keys ride .c only,by_n:2
    Assertion:idzeug-minted,sentence:Alice holds a single-use Idzeug — an unbound Music grant scoped to Classical,by_n:3
    Assertion:tamper-rejected,sentence:a tampered Idzeug fails verification — one flipped signature byte and it is rejected,by_n:4
    Assertion:offline-redeem-fails,sentence:redeeming with the inviter offline fails — the Idzeug is proof of receipt not an offline token,by_n:4
    Assertion:page-imported,sentence:Bob imported the page of Alice — the stashed Peering reborn under his Pier,by_n:5
    Assertion:reciprocity-sealed,sentence:each Pier carries a Music grant the OTHER signed — Classical only — reciprocity sealed,by_n:5
    Assertion:friendship-edge,sentence:the friendship is an edge logged in the social graph at both ends,by_n:5
    Assertion:single-use-spent,sentence:the Idzeug is single-use — a second redeem finds the nonce spent and is rebuffed,by_n:6
    Assertion:notgrant-retires,sentence:a NotGrant under the Pier retires it at use — the other end stands until told,by_n:7
    Assertion:account-roundtrip,sentence:the account survives export and import byte for byte — Pier and grants and keys intact,by_n:8
